                                        Angular

                                    Bank app in angular

                                    Fornt end: angular
                                    Backend: node.js(express)
                                    Database:mongodb

            Basic bulding blocks
            
            1.module-to import 3rd party libraries
            2.components -to create html css and ts files

            Basic commands

            1.create aproject-> ng new project name
            2.create a cmponent->  ng g c component name
            3.Run-> ng serve --open

      1)Data binding

        To share data inside the components

        ts-component and html-view

        1)one way data binding (ts->html or html ->ts file)

            a)component to view
                a.1) string interpolation-{{expression}}
                a.2) property binding -[attribute_name]="property"

            b)view to component
                 b.1) event binding - (event_name)="function name"
                 b.2) event binding using $event - (event_name)="function name($event)"
                 
                        
           